import React from 'react'
import UnitColumn from './UnitColumn'
import { Box } from '@mui/material'

function DiceRollerPage() {
  return (
    <Box sx={{display: 'flex', maxWidth: '80%', border: 1}}>
      <UnitColumn unit="Cruiser" index={0}></UnitColumn>
      <UnitColumn unit="Cruiser" index={0}></UnitColumn>
      <UnitColumn unit="Cruiser" index={0}></UnitColumn>
      <UnitColumn unit="Cruiser" index={0}></UnitColumn>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default DiceRollerPage
